category: Audio
requires: 
sdesc: "Cross platform audio output library (docs)"
ldesc: "Libao is a cross-platform audio library that allows programs to 
output audio using a simple API on a wide variety of platforms.  It 
currently supports:

   * Null output
   * WAV files
   * aRts (KDE sound daemon)
   * NAS (X11 networked sound daemon)
   * OSS (Open Sound System)
   * ESD (ESounD or Enlightened Sound Daemon)"
